section.para:
Using XPath syntax, the following is a list of values searched for type names

	//bp:bean/bp:argument/@type
	//bp:bean/@class
	//bp:service/@interface
	//bp:reference/@interface
	//bp:reference-list/@interface
	//bp:map/@key-type
	//bp:map/@value-type
	//bp:list/@value-type
	//bp:set/@value-type
	//bp:array/@value-type
	//bp:interfaces/bp:value
